00:16:00,034 --> 00:16:03,068
♪ Silly old willy
old Christmas bear ♪

349
00:16:03,103 --> 00:16:04,517
♪ He couldn't sleep a wink

350
00:16:04,551 --> 00:16:05,793
♪ And he couldn't think

