00:16:09,344 --> 00:16:12,275
♪ Winslow the Christmas bear

353
00:16:12,310 --> 00:16:15,275
♪ Funny old sunny
old Christmas bear ♪

354
00:16:15,310 --> 00:16:18,448
♪ He doesn't even know
where he ought to go ♪

355
00:16:18,482 --> 00:16:23,413
♪ On this Christmas Eve

356
00:16:23,448 --> 00:16:26,172
♪ He doesn't know
